title: Frieze, 1905–15
inscribed: Printed in top selvedge, "Robert S. Hobbs & Co." pattern number "2616".
description: Art nouveau. Spiraling and scrolling medallions connected by vining with large flowers. Bottom band of waving scrolls/spirals. Printed on light beige ground in beige, light green, red-brown, pink-brown, metallic gold and metallic copper. Printed in top selvedge, "Robert S. Hobbs & Co." pattern number "2616".

tombstone.epitaph:
Frieze, 1905–15.
1905–15. Machine-printed, mica. Gift of Victorian Collectibles. 1979-91-517.
